For your current bundle layout, the key variable is this:

aerolit_bundle_root: "/path/to/opened/aerolit_bundle"

Then the role automatically uses:

pxe_content_iso_root: "{{ aerolit_bundle_root }}/extracted_isos"
pxe_content_image_tar_path: "{{ aerolit_bundle_root }}/files/pxe/pxe-content.tar"

So in your screenshot example, if the bundle root is:

/root/aerolit_rhel8_standard

then the role will mount:

/root/aerolit_rhel8_standard/extracted_isos:/iso:ro,Z

That is the piece that fixes the /iso versus extracted_isos confusion. Host side is extracted_isos; container side stays /iso.